{
  "stem": "12612.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know where my father was at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the Russians came upstairs to us and took my mother around the waist and said, the Germans we take by force.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Jews we take with love.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, he must have spoken a little Yiddish or else my mother wouldn't have been able to understand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, my god, give me-- give me a sign.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How am I going to get out of this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she screamed, typhus typhus!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the guy was so scared of getting typhoid fever that he ran down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He almost broke his neck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you remember this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This my mother told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Trobitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1945.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somewhere between May and April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember being in army trucks, hoarded in army trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know if that was to get to Bergen-Belsen, or if that was to get to the train, or if that was to get from Trobitz to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I somehow get the feeling that it was to go to the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I remember was it was an open army truck, you know, nothing on top of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were all squished in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Skinny.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of us had typhoid fever, [INAUDIBLE], and [INAUDIBLE] fever, typhoid fever, very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they shaved us completely bald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess the nurses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, they-- the Dutch people gave us a certificate to come back, that we were allowed to come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave us a house on the same street-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] on the same side, as a matter of fact-- down the block from where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
